{
  "text": "Monobulks: Unblended, monovalent lots of subunit vaccine antigen were produced in embryonated chicken eggs by Novartis Vaccines (now Seqirus) in either pilot or engineering batches as previously described [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
